      • setUp

        public void setUp()
           throws Exception
        Fills some test data into the configuration and creates the tree model. The test data consists of a root node representing a tables element. It has children representing a single table each. The tables are named with the prefix ELEM_TABLE and a numeric index. Each table element has a number of field elements as children that are also named using a prefix (ELEM_FIELD) and a numeric index.
        Throws:
        Exception
